&lt;p&gt;Due to the promotion of the current post-holder, there is a vacancy for a motivated and experienced Speech &amp; Language Therapist to join the team on the Acute Stroke &amp; Rehabilitation Unit (ASRU) at Blackpool Victoria Hospital. The suitable candidate should be competent in assessment and management of both communication and swallowing difficulties and have an interest in acute and early rehabilitation of stroke. They will join a well-established multi-disciplinary team on the Unit and will work closely with other SLTs and SLT Assistants as well as being part of the Adult SLT team.&lt;/p&gt;
